    "long_instructions": "Dan was playing around with sounds and discovered a groove that he liked, but when he walked away from his computer his little sister ran over and pulled apart all the blocks. Can you help him put his song back together?\r\n\r\nDan: \"I had the Steady Drums sound and the Muted Guitar together, and then I had the Full Drums and Instruments together\"\r\n\r\nCan you reconstruct his song?",
